productBaseInfoV1.title: Sony PSP 4 GB(Black)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Game on the move with the affordable and technologically advanced Sony PSP. Keep yourself entertained  by playing your favorite games while travelling or while waiting around for someone. The Sony PSP E1004 bundle with the Sony 4 GB Produo Card lets you save the progress of your game and continue from where you paused. This handheld gaming console has been designed for hard core gamers who love to game wherever they go. The PSP also allows you to carry your favorite music, movies and photos in this ergonomically designed gadget. The Sony PSP is the only handheld gaming console that uses the optical disc format as its primary storage medium. The PSP's ability to connect to other multimedia devices such as the PlayStation 2, PlayStation 3 and other PSPs for multiplayer action make it very user-friendly and engaging. Multimedia features are greatly enhanced through faster screen refresh rates and superior color reproduction. Design and Power The Sony PSP  E1004 is ergonomically designed to fit snugly in your palms and it has dimensions of 170 x 23 x 74 mm making it very easy to carry around. The light weight design of the PSP E1004 weighs only 280 g including the battery pack. Enjoy brilliant visuals on the 4.3 inch (10.9 cm) screen with a color resolution of 16,770,000 dots. The TFT LCD screen has an aspect ratio of 16:9 and is a Full-Transparent Type display. The control keys are divided on both sides of the console and the screen is located in between them. The keys on the right side of the PSP are dedicated to control actions like accelerate, shoot and attack, while the keys on the left side are used to control the direction in which your characters moves. The D-Pad or direction pad of the PSP is designed to allow free movement of the thumb across all 4 buttons. This feature allows you to change direction and react to any surprises in the game. Both keypads are ergonomically designed to reduce any strain on your fingers while playing. The console also has an analog pad for gamers who are more comfortable with joystick gaming.  Additional buttons are provided on the on the top corners of the Sony PSP E1004 for easy access with the index finger. These shoulder buttons provide additional in-game control options. The PSP E1004 comes with a USB 2.0 port which helps you connect this handheld device to your computer. Enjoy your game privately even in crowded areas by plugging in your headphones. For added functionality Sony has included an IR port on this PSP. The PSP E1004 has a rechargeable lithium-ion battery which can provide several hours of fun on a single charge. The battery life depends on the function of the PSP that you use the most. Use the AC adapter to recharge the battery or just play with the adapter plugged in for uninterrupted game play. While recharging the battery, the PSP E1004 has a power consumption of 6W. Performance and Connectivity Multiplayer games with human opponents are more fun as players are able to adapt and play more diverse moves when compared to the standard AI of the computer. Party with friends by playing music out loud on this PSP. The Monaural Speaker is clear when playing music and game effects. The inbuilt Read-only Universal Media Disc drive or UMD drive is capable of storing images, videos and music in various formats. You can use your PSP as a portable photo viewer, MP3 player and portable movie player while you are visiting friends or travelling somewhere. This portable device is perfect for people who are constantly on the move. This Sony PSP E1004 is bundled with a Sony  4 GB Produo Card for extra memory to store additional information. Carry more than one Produo Card to ensure you have all the entertainment you need while you travel. Take your entertainment wherever you travel and never be bored again. Play online games and catch up with your gamer friends. Play single player games when alone and switch to multiplayer mode when you meet up with your friends. The PSP lets you carry your entertainment in a safe and portable manner while ensuring that only high quality visuals and audio is delivered to the user.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Razer Tron Wired USB Gaming Keyboard
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Disney’s Tron: Legacy [2010] is about a young kid who delves into his father’s work of computer coding only to find his father living in a virtual world created by him. The futuristic feel with streaks of light and the sound effects captured the imagination of the Razer design team who collaborated with Disney Consumer Products team to release this beautiful piece of high performance gadgetry. Each Razer Tron Keyboard features a luminescent blue glow that reminds us fans of the epic battles and gear used in the film. The Razer Tron is a wired keyboard that has state-of-the-art features that will pull gamers and coders alike into the digital world of the Tron universe. The super smooth and durable finish of this Razer Tron Keyboard ensures that it will make your gamer friends go green with envy. The Razer Tron Keyboard also has a very cool start up effect with the keyboard lighting up from the left to the right accompanied by sound effects straight from the movie. Style and Portability The Razer Tron Keyboard is much larger than most contemporary keyboards with dimensions of 458 x 170 x 31 mm. The larger surface area allowed Razer to optimize the space between the keys and travel distance between keys. The flat design of the Chiclet keys allows you to glide your finger over to the next key for immediate actuation of commands. This 1520 gram Razer keyboard is designed to be a heavy-duty gaming accessory that can take the constant pounding of a gamer engrossed in completing the mission at hand. The Razer Tron Keyboard can be used to play in the dark or in low light conditions as it has comes with Tron inspired blue backlights and sidestrips. You have the option of switching off the lighting feature based on your preferences. The modular numeric pad can be detached from the right side of the keyboard and can be attached to the left side by using the connector. This feature is meant to give you additional keys on the left side for you to program macros. The USB cable that connects the Razer Tron Keyboard to the system is braided making it durable and safe from damage. The Chiclet keys of the Razer keyboard are hyperresponsive to ensure that your instructions are being quickly followed to the letter. Performance The braided USB cable of the Razer Tron Keyboard has 2 USB ports that need to be connected to 2 separate USB ports on your system. Along with the USB cable a microphone in and audio-out is also present, which if plugged in will allow you to connect your microphone and headphone to the keyboard. The Razer Tron Keyboard works well with computers operating on Windows 7, Vista and XP. Gaming mode can be activated on the Razer Tron Keyboard to disable the Windows button which normally interferes with game play by pulling up the Windows menu. Macro keys can be recorded on any key of the Razer Tron Keyboard except the Function keys. Macros are a sequence of keystrokes that can be executed in a particular order and timing by pressing a single button. Besides Macro key setting, profiles can also be stored to allow you to quickly access different key settings for different games. The media keys are function keys F5 to F8 located on top in the centre for quick and easy access while playing multimedia content on your PC. The response of the Razer Tron Keyboard is lighting quick as it has 1000 Hz ultrapolling and a 1 ms response time. To complete the entire Tron gaming setup, you can also buy the supercool Tron gaming mouse and mouse pad which is also designed by Razer. The minimum system requirements to install this Razer Tron Keyboard is a PC with 2 hi-speed USB ports, Windows operating system and 35 MB of free hard disk space. Also make sure you register your Razer products at www.razerzone.com/registration so that you are kept aware of new software updates.
